Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-真想…\N- 4
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再看一次…\N- 2
