Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"越是想要见你"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"铁锈味越是在心中扩散"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"因为寒气而无法动弹的手"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"究竟能做什么"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"我只能祈祷"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,基地的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是基地的樱花…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,(12月25日 15点27分)
